  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Semi-Permanent Roofing and Apprenticeship Program</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ConPRmetidos, along with Heart 9/11 and the University of the Sacred Heart, have agreed to partner in a project to repair or replace damaged roofs in the communities of Playita and Cantera Peninsula in Puerto Rico using volunteers provided by HEART 9/11 and apprentices recruited by Sacred Heart. The Program contains three components: (1) damage assessment and inventory; (2) recruitment, training, and management of fifteen apprentices; and (3) installation of fifty semi-permanent roofs.</narrative>
  </description>
